ven"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taA^ax~ira Eanohu taA^ax~urapF waAHidapF", "text_ar": "تَاَخِّرَ عَنْهُ تَاَخُّرَةً وَاحِدَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He went back,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, once"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Lh.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tA^x~r Eani Al$~aYo'i", "text_ar": "تاخّر عَنِ الشَّىْءِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA^amori", "text_ar": "الاَمْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He went back,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from the thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the affair: he was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, behind, behindhand,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "backward, with respect to it: he held back, hung back, refrained,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "abstained, from it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eanohu", "text_ar": "عَنْهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AstA^xr", "text_ar": "استاخر", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the same. (The Lexicons in many places.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faA_i*aA jaA='a", "text_ar": "فَاـِذَا جَا=ءَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEapF", "text_ar": "سَاعَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ajaluhumo laA yasotaA^oxiruwna", "text_ar": "اَجَلُهُمْ لَا يَسْتَاْخِرُونَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the Kur vii. 32 and other places, means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And when their time is come,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "for punishment,"}, {"kind": 